<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 12:44:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>由于对伊朗可能停火的乐观情绪，比特币突破 70,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/bitcoin-ticks-up-even-as-trump-s-iran-war-threats-cloud-markets</link><description>周一，比特币自 3 月 25 日以来首次回升至 70,000 美元以上，投资者权衡有关伊朗正在寻求在持续战争中停火的报道，尽管美国总统唐纳德·特朗普升级了攻击民用基础设施的威胁。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i_9FadNWL_HQ/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 02:50:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-06/bitcoin-ticks-up-even-as-trump-s-iran-war-threats-cloud-markets</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织警告代币化金融风险加剧未来市场危机</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-04/imf-warns-tokenized-finance-risks-amplifying-market-crises-ahead</link><description>国际货币基金组织表示，将华尔街的交易基础设施转移到基于区块链的系统上可能会加速金融危机，超出监管机构的应对能力，尽管该技术有望削减成本并消除结算延迟。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEArrMoKZyzU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-04/imf-warns-tokenized-finance-risks-amplifying-market-crises-ahead</guid></item></channel></rss>